    <Overview name="Overview0">
      <links/>
      <content><![CDATA[<p>In OpenCms content and layout are strictly separated. To render content of a special content type, several formatters can be provided. Each formatter can be configured to be used according to the container where the content is placed.</p>
<p>We explore the basic structure of a formatter and shown in detail how to configure it.</p>]]></content>
    </Overview>
    <Teaser name="Teaser0">
      <links/>
      <content><![CDATA[<p>Find out how to render content with formatters and how to configure various formatters for content of the same type.</p>]]></content>
    </Teaser>
